Data set source:
https://github.com/jookriha/M_Spheres_Dataset_Generator

Description: 
Generates multidimensional random points that are on the
M-dimensional sphere centered on c with radius of d. 

Reference:
J. H‰m‰l‰inen, T. K‰rkk‰inen, and T. Rossi, "Improving scalable k-
means++", Algorithms, 14(1), 2021.

